00:12:49,936 --> 00:12:52,146
Do me favor and try not to die.

248
00:12:54,649 --> 00:12:57,485
I don't want to have
to reap your souls.

249
00:12:59,445 --> 00:13:01,948
Putting the crazy Skeletor
doppelganger aside,

250
00:13:01,990 --> 00:13:03,908
I'm actually kinda surprised
that Lord Zeus

251
00:13:03,950 --> 00:13:05,910
and Lord Poseidon
are gonna be there.

252
00:13:05,952 --> 00:13:08,288
I'm not. That's how much
attention this game is getting.

253
00:13:08,329 --> 00:13:09,831
‐[door opens]
‐[RISER] Excuse me.

254
00:13:09,872 --> 00:13:12,333
Hello. I'm here for the match.

255
00:13:12,375 --> 00:13:14,127
‐Huh.
‐[gasps]

256
00:13:14,168 --> 00:13:16,629
‐[gasps]
‐Whoa! Riser?

257
00:13:16,671 --> 00:13:17,672
Big brother?

258
00:13:19,132 --> 00:13:21,926
