to show off your strength here.

261
00:13:27,181 --> 00:13:28,975
It would certainly make
a strong point.

262
00:13:29,934 --> 00:13:31,519
I'm more nervous than excited,

263
00:13:31,561 --> 00:13:34,105
since I'm not as talented
as Sona in battle tactics,

264
00:13:34,147 --> 00:13:36,482
nor am I as powerful
as Lord Sairaorg.

265
00:13:36,524 --> 00:13:39,444
All I have is
a wonderful family.

266
00:13:39,485 --> 00:13:42,071
Battle tactics and strength
are all well and good,

267
00:13:42,113 --> 00:13:44,073
but they're both something
that anyone can gain

268
00:13:44,115 --> 00:13:46,075
with enough experience
and effort.

269
00:13:46,117 --> 00:13:48,411
And more importantly,
someone who has

270
00:13:48,453 --> 00:13:50,455
a natural talent
for finding and gathering

271
00:13:50,496 --> 00:13:52,081
skilled individuals
is special.

272
00:13:52,123 --> 00:13:54,959
I honestly believe
it's that particular ability

273
00:13:55,001 --> 00:13:56,627
which has given you
the wonderful family

274
00:13:56,669 --> 00:13:58,713
