to boast about, Rias.

275
00:13:58,755 --> 00:14:02,550
Perhaps, but they could also
be here just because of Issei.

276
00:14:02,592 --> 00:14:05,178
You're the one who recruited
the Red Dragon Emperor,

277
00:14:05,219 --> 00:14:08,306
so it's still because of you.
Take a look around.

278
00:14:08,348 --> 00:14:09,974
[footsteps]

279
00:14:10,016 --> 00:14:13,144
See? These people
are here to support you,

280
00:14:13,186 --> 00:14:15,563
because you all
share something.

281
00:14:15,605 --> 00:14:17,523
Believe in their strength.

282
00:14:17,565 --> 00:14:18,983
[gasps]

283
00:14:19,025 --> 00:14:21,444
Hmm. I should go.

284
00:14:24,197 --> 00:14:26,282
‐Oh, and Red Dragon.
‐Huh?

285
00:14:26,324 --> 00:14:28,576
[RISER] I've never
forgotten the way it felt

286
00:14:28,618 --> 00:14:30,620
when you punched me
during our game.

287
00:14:30,661 --> 00:14:33,081
Know that I intend
to return the favor.

288
00:14:33,122 --> 00:14:35,291
But I can't do that
until you win this match

289
00:14:35,333 --> 00:14:37,210
and come up
to the professional league.

290
00:14:37,251 --> 00:14:39,212
Right! Don't you worry.

291
00:14:39,253 --> 00:14:41,672
Next time we battle, I'm gonna
wipe the floor with you.

292
00:14:41,714 --> 00:14:45,218
Also, you'd better
watch over my little sister.

293
00:14:45,259 --> 00:14:47,720
If you make her cry,
I will roast you alive

294
00:14:47,762 --> 00:14:48,888
and serve you for dinner.

295
00:14:48,930 --> 00:14:50,390
Eyes on the mini babe.

296
00:14:50,431 --> 00:14:52,266
‐You got it!
‐Uh, excuse me!

297
00:14:52,308 --> 00:14:53,726
He's not my keeper!

298
00:14:53,768 --> 00:14:57,063
[ALL laugh]

299
00:14:57,105 --> 00:14:58,815
Oh, that's right.

300
00:14:58,856 --> 00:15:00,983
I'm supposed to give you
a message from Sir Zechs.

301
00:15:01,025 --> 00:15:02,777
He said he needed
a moment of your time.

302
00:15:02,819 --> 00:15:03,778
Huh?

303
00:15:05,405 --> 00:15:07,448
Thank you for coming.
Your fans sent you

304
00:15:07,490 --> 00:15:09,659
a little something
that I wanted you to see.

305
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:11,869
Really? They did?
So what is it?

306
00:15:11,911 --> 00:15:14,539
Go on and take
a look for yourself.

307
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:16,707
I hope you win the game,
Grabbin' Dragon,

308
00:15:16,749 --> 00:15:18,084
and good luck out there!

309
00:15:18,126 --> 00:15:20,253
‐[KIDS] We love you!
‐[chuckles]

310
00:15:20,294 --> 00:15:21,504
‐Mr. Grabbin' Dragon...
‐Kapow!

311
00:15:21,546 --> 00:15:22,797
‐...you're the coolest!
‐Take that!

312
00:15:22,839 --> 00:15:24,757
‐Summon Tig Ol' Bitties! Yay!
‐Boop, boop, go!

313
00:15:24,799 --> 00:15:26,926
‐[laughs]
‐Balance break! Yeah!

314
00:15:26,968 --> 00:15:29,804
Do your best, today!
I'll be cheering you on as loud

315
00:15:29,846 --> 00:15:33,182
as I can from home, okay?
I hope you win! [laughs]

316
00:15:33,224 --> 00:15:35,601
This is what
I wanted to show you.

317
00:15:35,643 --> 00:15:37,437
Children from all
over the Underworld

318
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:41,149
will be watching tonight.
They admire you, Issei.

319
00:15:41,190 --> 00:15:43,860
No matter what,
there will always be

320
00:15:43,901 --> 00:15:45,903
adult politics in these games.

321
00:15:45,945 --> 00:15:48,531
That's how matches
have always been.

322
00:15:48,573 --> 00:15:52,034
Even so, I'd like to be
so bold as to ask you a favor.

323
00:15:52,076 --> 00:15:54,412
If at all possible,
can you please fight

324
00:15:54,454 --> 00:15:56,122
for the dreams
of these children?

325
00:15:56,164 --> 00:15:58,583
And while it's important
to protect their dreams,

326
00:15:58,624 --> 00:16:02,670
I hope you'll fight just
as hard to protect your own.

327
00:16:02,712 --> 00:16:04,046
Yeah, of course I will.

328
00:16:04,088 --> 00:16:07,049
Because after all,
I am the Grabbin' Dragon!

329
00:16:16,058 --> 00:16:20,146
[CROWD cheering, applauding]

330
00:16:20,188 --> 00:16:22,148
